file: RunEventStore.php
class: "Ineersa\\AgentCore\\Infrastructure\\Storage\\RunEventStore"
type: final class
summary: The RunEventStore provides a persistence layer for RunEvent entities within the infrastructure storage boundary. It abstracts the underlying storage mechanism to allow appending individual or batched events and retrieving the complete event history for a specific run. This class serves as the primary interface for run-related event data access and mutation.
